<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,255,1821,1843]" pageId="2" pageNumber="232">FIGURE 1.</emphasis>
Illustration 
<emphasis box="[374,606,1821,1842]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="232">
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="A. Cadiz-Veliz" authorityYear="2021" box="[399,606,1821,1842]" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Miersia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="2" pageNumber="232" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="putaendensis">Miersia putaendensis</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
: (A) Habit, (B) Detail of flower (frontal view), (C) Detail of flower (lateral view), (D) Fruit (lateral view), (E) Fruit (apical view), (F) Fruit (medial transverse section), and (G) Seed. Drawn by Arón Cádiz-Véliz.
